---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Experiences – Yoonchul Yi">
  <main class="py-8 space-y-12">
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text">
        Experiences
      </h1>
      <div class="h-px bg-border/60"></div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Business Research @
            <a
              href="https://www.rlwrld.ai/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-sub hover:text-accent hover:underline transition-colors"
            >
              RLWRLD
            </a>
            <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-sub mt-1">
              2025.10. – 2026.01.
            </span>
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90 space-y-1">
            <li>
              Structured global partner requirements into feasible PoC scenarios
              to align with technical capabilities.
            </li>
            <li>
              Established a pioneering dexterity benchmark taxonomy based on
              real-world industrial use cases.
            </li>
            <li>
              Informed R&amp;D and business strategies by analyzing global
              robotics trends and competitor insights.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Sergeant @ Republic of Korea Army
            <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-sub mt-1">
              2023.01. – 2024.07.
            </span>
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            Provided transportation and operational support within a
            counter-intelligence unit.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Mechanical Engineering @ Seoul National University
            <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-sub mt-1">
              2021.03. –
            </span>
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            Participated in web and app development clubs, and the SNU Student
            Venture Network (36th cohort).
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text">
        Projects
      </h1>
      <div class="h-px bg-border/60"></div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Storybook4me
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            Developing a personalized AI storybook service that transforms
            family memories into high-quality, fully illustrated children's
            tales. WIP, experimental weekend build.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://storybook4.me"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-sub hover:text-accent hover:underline transition-colors"
          >
            learn more ↗
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Mynovel
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            Developed a full-stack AI platform that transforms ideas into
            full-length novel drafts. Architected a 6-step generative pipeline
            using <span class="font-semibold">LangChain</span> and
            <span class="font-semibold">FastAPI</span>, incorporating research
            from 60+ papers to improve <span class="font-semibold">EQ-Bench</span>
            scores. Conducted on-site user research with writer communities in
            the SF Bay Area to identify core user needs and refine product
            direction.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://getmynovel.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-sub hover:text-accent hover:underline transition-colors"
          >
            learn more ↗
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Notion Templates
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            I design and sell Notion templates to boost personal productivity.
            Many templates are free, feel free to take a look!
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.notion.com/ko/@aidenyi"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-sub hover:text-accent hover:underline transition-colors"
          >
            learn more ↗
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Leadliner
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            A service that used AI to summarize daily news for selected stocks.
            The service is currently discontinued.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/yyoonchul/leadliner_web"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-sub hover:text-accent hover:underline transition-colors"
          >
            learn more ↗
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Content Creation &amp; Management
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            I run a newsletter that introduces the hottest early-stage U.S.
            startups to the Korean startup community. Within its first month,
            the newsletter achieved a combined 10k views across two platforms.
            I also managed an Instagram account, where I curated startup-related
            books and articles into bite-sized content, growing the account to
            1.6k followers over a year before it was archived.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text">
        Skillset
      </h1>
      <div class="h-px bg-border/60"></div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <article class="space-y-1">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            FastAPI
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            While I vibe code in any language these days, I specialize in
            Python and primarily use FastAPI.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="space-y-1">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-lg text-text">
            Notion
          </h2>
          <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/90">
            Experience in designing and selling productivity templates (30k+
            downloads).
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

